    <body>
        <p>You can use macros in <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> to automate frequently used commands or processes. After you record a macro, you can play it back to perform all of the steps in the macro with a single action. You can also assign a shortcut to the macro<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.FlareOnlineOnly"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Shortcuts/Changing-Hot-Keys.htm">Changing Hot Keys</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.ContributorOnlineOnly"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Contributor/Shortcuts/Changing-Hot-Keys.htm">Changing Hot Keys</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>, add it to the Quick Access Toolbar<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.FlareOnlineOnly"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Interface/Quick-Access-Toolbar.htm">Quick Access Toolbar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.ContributorOnlineOnly"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Contributor/Interface/Quick-Access-Toolbar.htm">Quick Access Toolbar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>, or access it from the Quick Launch bar<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.FlareOnlineOnly"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Interface/UI-Elements/Quick-Launch-Bar.htm">Quick Launch Bar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.ContributorOnlineOnly"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Contributor/Interface/UI-Elements/Quick-Launch-Bar.htm">Quick Launch Bar</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>.  Macros save you time by streamlining the repetitive tasks you do every day, freeing you up for other tasks.</p>
